longBusinessSummary: Dolly Varden Silver Corporation engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in Canada. The company explores for gold, silver, lead, zinc, and copper deposits. It holds 100% interests in the Dolly Varden project covering an area of 8,800 hectares; and the Big Bulk property located in Canada. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
